<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>你的名字 | 个人主页</title>
    <!-- 引入 Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- 引入 Lucide Icons CDN，用于美观的图标 -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6; /* 背景色 */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-gray-800">

    <!-- 导航栏 -->
    <nav class="bg-white sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-md">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="#hero" class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 transition duration-300">你的名字</a>
            <div class="space-x-4 hidden md:flex">
                <a href="#about" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition duration-300">关于我</a>
                <a href="#skills" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition duration-300">技能</a>
                <a href="#projects" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition duration-300">项目</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition duration-300">联系</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container mx-auto">

        <!-- 英雄区 -->
        <section id="hero" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-8 bg-white md:bg-transparent">
            <div class="text-center md:text-left md:w-1/2">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-gray-900 mb-4 animate-fade-in">
                    你好，我是 <br class="md:hidden">
                    <span class="text-indigo-600">你的名字</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto md:mx-0">
                    一位充满热情的 <span class="font-semibold">[你的职业/身份]</span>，致力于创建 <span class="font-semibold">[你的目标/领域]</span>。
                </p>
                <a href="#projects" class="bg-indigo-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
                    查看我的作品
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-12 md:mt-0 md:w-1/2 flex justify-center animate-zoom-in">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/400x400/94a3b8/ffffff?text=你的照片" alt="你的照片" class="rounded-full shadow-xl w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 object-cover border-4 border-white">
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 关于我 -->
        <section id="about" class="py-20 px-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg mt-12 md:mt-24">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">关于我</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:space-x-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/3 mb-8 md:mb-0">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/300x300/475569/ffffff?text=关于图片" alt="关于我" class="rounded-lg shadow-md">
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        在这里写一些关于你自己的详细介绍。比如你的工作经历、教育背景、技能专长，以及你的个人爱好和生活理念等等。
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        你的座右铭或者一个有趣的事实。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 技能 -->
        <section id="skills" class="py-20 px-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">我的技能</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                <!-- 技能项 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-code text-indigo-500 mb-4"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">编程</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">JavaScript, Python, React, ...</p>
                </div>
                <!-- 技能项 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-pen-tool text-indigo-500 mb-4"><path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z"/><path d="M18.5 13.5L5 19 2 16 15.5 2.5 18.5 5.5z"/><path d="M2 16l4.5-4.5"/><path d="M4.5 13.5l4.5-4.5"/></svg>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">设计</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">UI/UX 设计, Figma, Photoshop, ...</p>
                </div>
                <!-- 更多技能... -->
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 项目 -->
        <section id="projects" class="py-20 px-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg mt-12 md:mt-24">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">我的项目</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- 项目卡片 -->
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/400x250/cbd5e1/ffffff?text=项目一图片" alt="项目一" class="rounded-md mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">项目一名称</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                        这是一个项目的简短描述。说明你做了什么，使用了什么技术，以及它有什么独特之处。
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="text-indigo-600 font-semibold hover:underline transition duration-300">
                        查看项目 &rarr;
                    </a>
                </div>
                <!-- 项目卡片 -->
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/400x250/cbd5e1/ffffff?text=项目二图片" alt="项目二" class="rounded-md mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">项目二名称</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                        这是另一个项目的简短描述。同样可以突出你的贡献和项目的亮点。
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="text-indigo-600 font-semibold hover:underline transition duration-300">
                        查看项目 &rarr;
                    </a>
                </div>
                <!-- 更多项目... -->
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 联系我 -->
        <section id="contact" class="py-20 px-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">联系我</h2>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    如果你对我的作品感兴趣，或者有合作意向，请随时通过以下方式联系我：
                </p>
                <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6">
                    <a href="mailto:你的邮箱@example.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 transition duration-300 flex items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-mail mr-2"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
                        <span>邮箱</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/你的github" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 transition duration-300 flex items-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-github mr-2"><path d="M15 22s-4 0-5-3c0 0-1-2 2-3s4-2 4-3c0-3-1-4-2-4s-3 1-4 2c-1-1-3-2-5-2c-2 0-3 1-4 3c-1 2-2 4-2 6c0 2 1 3 2 3c-1 0-2 0-3-1c-1-1-2-2-2-4s-1-3-1-3c0-1 0-2 1-2c0 0-1-1-1-3s-1-2-1-3c0-1 1-1 2-1c1 0 2 1 3 2c1 1 2 2 3 2s2-1 3-2c1-1 2-2 3-2c1 0 2 1 2 2c0 1 0 2 0 3c0 2-1 3-2 3c-1 0-2 0-3 1z"/></svg>
                        <span>GitHub</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- 页脚 -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white text-center p-6 mt-12">
        <p>&copy; 2025 你的名字. 保留所有权利。</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
